lead_paragraph: Dak Prescott can help the Dallas Cowboys set a franchise record with 14 wins. Ezekiel Elliott could break Eric Dickerson's 33-year-old rookie rushing record with a career high and a few more yards.

headline.print_headline: Rookie Stars Want Wins, Even With Cowboys Secure Atop NFC
